            "title": "亞洲三鐵半奧運距離錦標賽｜港將伍泰龍、韋祺分奪男、女子組第9 寄望周日混合賽上頒獎台",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"港將伍泰龍、韋祺分奪男、女子組第9 周日混合賽全力爭上頒獎台。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c176cb6f41f5f58607effb41b6a35920/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040515083912501.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">港將伍泰龍、韋祺分奪男、女子組第9 周日混合賽全力爭上頒獎台。徐嘉華攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>作為香港全運會第一個選拔賽的「亞洲三鐵半奧運距離錦標賽」周六早上在中環大雨下進行個人賽，港隊的伍泰龍及韋祺同樣以第9名完成男、女子組個人賽，在3個全運選拔賽中稍佔上風，他們周日將出戰男女混合接力賽，期望登上頒獎台。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"杭州亞運金牌的日本選手北條巧(中)以53分19秒奪男子組冠軍。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21c52924143cf5ed51ac5da356a8ec93/2025-04/2_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        杭州亞運金牌的日本選手北條巧(中)以53分19秒奪男子組冠軍。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"中國的林鑫瑜(中)以59分07秒於女子組奪冠。徐嘉華\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/742c6a5e79ed0080db900865ed8335eb/2025-04/2_0_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        中國的林鑫瑜(中)以59分07秒於女子組奪冠。徐嘉華\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧斯卡(後2)與季軍中國范俊杰(前2)跑在同一群。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/385984e8c36eb1972c9b11edc19e2145/2025-04/174383597162055.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧斯卡(後2)與季軍中國范俊杰(前2)跑在同一群。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧斯卡衝線一刻。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cbf7c6d6831b9882584727ffe653951/2025-04/174383597150052.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧斯卡衝線一刻。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧斯卡進行單車部份比賽。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99662e6891bad66be2ac6d91d0328db7/2025-04/2_1_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧斯卡進行單車部份比賽。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男子組跳水起步。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https