            "title": "尖沙咀巴士撼的士  巴士車頭嚴重損毀",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"巴士車頭嚴重損毀。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/063579616de15e4edb998621028c240a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040514564297284.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">巴士車頭嚴重損毀。fb：車cam L（香港群組）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（5日）午2時許，一輛巴士沿尖沙咀北京道往佐敦方向行駛，在北京道一號時與一輛的士相撞，巴士擋風玻璃爆裂及車頭嚴重損毀，慶幸事件中無人受傷，受事故影響，現場交通擠塞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4178248/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"巴士與的士相撞。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/13f4da809385c4a66ae5511e01c12fd9/2025-04/01_2_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴士與的士相撞。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
