            "title": "鰂魚涌華蘭花園梯間煤氣樽藏垃圾桶起火爆炸 消防調查認為有可疑",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/994a35af1da522ba14dae761b57cafac/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040514535929864.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>鰂魚涌華蘭路7號華蘭花園，今（5日)中午1時18分，保安報案指樓上梯間位置，有垃圾桶起火，內有煤氣樽，曾起火爆炸，消防接報到場，火勢已熄滅，經調查後認為起火原因有可疑。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4178239/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a36cb9eb3940c9c5ed0d26043a56e9ed/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_140859450.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4178240/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為華蘭花園梯間位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2caaf89f8f3e94b329b744c3507166cc/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250405_140859450_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\